## Description {#details}

----------------—<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/aaintrafnreachability">AAIntraFnReachability</a> Attribute-----------------------—

All information associated with a reachability query. This boilerplate code is used by both <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/aaintrafnreachability">AAIntraFnReachability</a> and <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/aainterfnreachability">AAInterFnReachability</a>, with different <code>ToTy</code> values.
